**Conditional Statements**

**if statement:**
```javascript
if (condition) {
    // Code runs if condition is true
}
```

**else statement:**
```javascript
if (condition) {
    // Runs if true
} else {
    // Runs if false
}
```

**Example with else:**
```javascript
function testElse(val) {
    var result;
    if (val > 20 || val < 10) {
        result = "OUTSIDE";
    } else {
        result = "INSIDE";
    }
    return result;
}
```

**else if statement:**
```javascript
function testElseIf(val) {
    let result;
    if (val > 20) {
        result = "OUTSIDE - above";
    } else if (val < 10) {
        result = "OUTSIDE - below";
    } else {
        result = "INSIDE";
    }
    return result;
}
```

**Chaining if/else if:**
```javascript
function getSize(val) {
    if (val < 5) {
        return "small";
    } else if (val < 10) {
        return "medium";
    } else if (val < 20) {
        return "large";
    } else {
        return "extra large";
    }
}
```

